  <brief_title>Activation of Alternative Cellular Energy (ACE) Pathway in the Therapy of Herpes Virus Infections</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Research Study Examining the Effectiveness of Distant Activation of ACE Pigments Associated With Recurrent Human Herpes Simplex Virus-Induced Skin Lesions.</official_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
      <agency>Institute of Progressive Medicine</agency>
