    <has_dmc>Yes</has_dmc>
  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The research question to be addressed is whether indirect phototherapy based activation of
      the body's alternative cellular energy (ACE) pathway will lead to expedited healing of active
      herpes simplex virus (HSV) and herpes zoster virus (HZV)skin lesions, and also possibly
      inhibit both latent HSV infections and residual HZV infections.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
